tory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:178: ## Operator layer do S3\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:180: A operator layer do S3 foi simplificada estruturalmente para 4 operators principais, mantendo uma taxonomy sem�ntica rica.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:182: ### Operators actuais\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:191: Os operators s�o respons�veis por:\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:197: Os operators **n�o** s�o respons�veis por:\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:201: - dedupe inter-operator global\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:204: Essas responsabilidades pertencem preferencialmente ao supervisor + substrate.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:208: ## Wiring: como o supervisor invoca os operators\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:212: O supervisor **n�o deve invocar os operators como fun��es internas Python**.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:227: Arquitecturalmente, o supervisor precisa de uma primitive equivalente a um **agent turn invoke**.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:240: ### O que o supervisor envia ao operator\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:242: O supervisor deve usar um modelo em duas camadas:\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:254: A mensagem enviada ao operator deve apontar para esse dispatch payload.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:266: O dispatch 