upervisor.md:19: ## Papel do supervisor\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:21: O `sm_s3_visual_planning` � o **control plane interno** do sector S3.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:25: O supervisor tamb�m n�o deve executar directamente a sem�ntica especializada dos operators.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:33: - invocar os operators correctos\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:39: ## O que o supervisor recebe no arranque\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:41: O supervisor deve ser activado com um bootstrap message contract estruturado, preparado pelo workflow do sector.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:53:   \"operators_dir\": \".../b2_s3_visual_planning/operators\",\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:62: ## Sequ�ncia inicial do supervisor\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:64: Quando o supervisor acorda, ele **n�o deve come�ar imediatamente pela sem�ntica**.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:70: O supervisor valida:\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:80: - o supervisor deve falhar limpo\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:82: - n�o deve prosseguir para dispatch de operators\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:88: Depois da valida��o do bootstrap, o supervisor deve marcar que o S3 foi formalmente assumido.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md:92: - `s3_supervisor_started.json`\r\nC:\\