 agent since its current behavior may not be updated. I'll make sure to look through those files and see if there are any key updates or directives regarding the ACP. This will help me understand any necessary changes in the agent's behavior. Let's get started on that!\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ebfmM2sHyl6VVDPKrXNtBYwh|fc_0f1f1c402b33ed570169cffce999e081918c93d2ec2128b964","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem -Force","workdir":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s3_visual_planning","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":30},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"Get-ChildItem -Force\",\"workdir\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\sm_s3_visual_planning\",\"yieldMs\":10000,\"timeout\":30}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7EshMAQVG6Gip94rOmqAuiYB|fc_0f1f1c402b33ed570169cffce999f08191bbaefff16a8820f0","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\SOUL.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\\\SOUL.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fZWW8wq0JsrzY4kCb8k7Yg6K|fc_0f1f1c402b33ed570169cffce999f8819199170d778f652614","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\USER.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\\\USER.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_la8lwydWpdTkfecLULATk2kD|fc_0f1f1c402b33ed570169cffce99a008191b732fa8d172fab13","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\CONTRACT.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\\\CONTRACT.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_mf2uBcPTOfcCJdUKZNW4sQ6p|fc_0f1f1c402b33ed570169cffce99a04819191d84100b377c97e","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\TOOLS.md"},"partialJso