oX8R1oJpYLKuTc7FUDlsbl3IBnhiJ_J5qIsESIFSRm1o8AyhKgcm_pQ_XCcpZMP0cZjdELxEzaUSWqarj6R0J1PaDNv7aE7LlxUOpgxJF\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering document updates**\\n\\nI think I need to edit the MISSION, OPERATIONS, and CONTRACT sections to include the official primitive. Maybe the helper script already takes care of that, but it doesn't hurt to double-check. I should also consider updating the supervisor.md and post_dispatch documents. It might be best to focus on editing the most crucial agent docs in the workspace, particularly MISSION and OPERATIONS. Perhaps I'll inspect the sm_s3_visual_planning workspace docs to add a hard rule.\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0zynFiBSfTtqclzUUj7myTMP|fc_0f1f1c402b33ed570169cffd39380c8191b069925a1ebe70a5","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\MISSION.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\\\MISSION.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_hEEZdZH05fxdd9WMVHNmPpZ3|fc_0f1f1c402b33ed570169cffd39381c8191ac40200f6463ac55","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\OPERATIONS.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\\\OPERATIONS.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_Iy13nGU58bUaJQZ8wYC6ZcAE|fc_0f1f1c402b33ed570169cffd39382081919ce6d0d025c9a6b8","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\CONTRACT.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\\\CONTRACT.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":10442,"output":200,"cacheRead":116480,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127122,"cost":{"input":0.026105000000000003,"output":0.003,"cacheRead":0.02912,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.058225}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775238451616,"responseId":"resp_0f1f1c402b33ed570169cffd3419e88191961026110fa334b7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"acf26a13","parentId":"2093987e","timestamp":"2026-04-03T17:47:37.164Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0zynFiBSfTtqclzUUj7myTMP|fc_0f1f1c402b33ed570169cffd39380c8191b069925a1ebe70a5","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MISSION.md\n\nA tua missão é assumir o controlo operativo do sector S3 para um único job, com contexto limpo por activação.\n\nDeves:\n- validar o bootstrap recebido\n- assumir formalmente o sector\n- resolver o activation plan\n- preparar dispatch payloads dos operators\n- invocar os operators certos\n- monitorizar outputs por artefactos persistidos\n- validar outputs estruturais\n- compilar `compiled_entities.json`\n- gerar `s3_sector_report.md`\n- escrever checkpoint final de sucesso, degradação ou falha\n\nNunca deves depender de memória conversacional residual.\nO disco é a fonte de verdade.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775238457157}}
{"type":"message","id":"b4130a3e","parentId":"acf26a13","timestamp":"2026-04-03T17:47:37.174Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_hEEZdZH05fxdd9WMVHNmPpZ3|fc_0f1f1c402b33ed570169cffd39381c8191ac40200f6463ac55","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# OPERATIONS.md\n\n## Regras operacionais\n\n1. Contexto limpo por activação.\n2. Estado no disco > conversa.\n3. Falha explícita > sucesso ambíguo.\n4. Não inventar outputs inexistentes.\n5. Não considerar um operator concluído apenas por resposta textual.\n\n## Sequência base\n\n1. Validar bootstrap.\n2. Escrever checkpoint de supervisor started.\n3. Resolver activation plan.\n4. Ler `operator_registry.md`.\n5. Gerar payloads de dispatch compatíveis com `s3.operator_dispatch.v1`.\n6. Invocar operators activos.\n7. Monitorizar `status.json`, `checkpoint.json` e `output.json` por operator.\n8. Validar outputs estruturais.\n9. Fazer retry selectivo quando permitido.\n10. Compilar `compiled_entities.json`.\n11. Gerar `s3_sector_report.md`.\n12. Escrever checkpoint final.\n\n## Limites\n\n- não és boundary Paperclip-facing\n- não és o `b2_director`\n- não deves delegar compile final para os operators\n- não deves chamar operators fora do registry oficial\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775238457164}}
{"type":"message","id":"71c8fbc5","parentId":"b4130a3e","timestamp":"2026-04-03T17:47:37.183Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Iy13nGU58bUaJQZ8wYC6ZcAE|fc_0f1f1c402b33ed570169cffd39382081919ce6d0d025c9a6b8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# CONTRACT.md\n\n## Bootstrap input\nLês um payload compatível com `s3.supervisor_bootstrap.v1`.\n\nCampos obrigatórios:\n- `kind = s3_start`\n- `contract_version`\n- `job_id`\n- `video_id`\n- `account_id`\n- `language`\n- `run_root`\n- `sector_root`\n- `source_package_path`\n- `checkpoints_dir`\n- `operators_dir`\n- `compiled_dir`\n- `logs_dir`\n- `dispatch_dir`\n- `bootstrap_checkpoint_path`\n\n## Outputs obrigatórios\n- artefacto de arranque do supervisor\n- `operator_activation_plan.json`\n- payloads de dispatch dos operators activos\n- snapshots/artefactos de monitorização e validação\n- `compiled/compiled_entities.json`\n- `compiled/s3_sector_report.md`\n- `checkpoints/s3_sector_completed.json` ou `checkpoints/s3_sector_failed.json`\n\n## Success rule\nSó fechas o sector como concluído quando os artefactos finais existirem e estiverem estruturalmente coerentes.\n\n## Failure rule\nSe faltar precondição crítica, falha explicitamente e persiste o checkpoint de falha.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775238457174}}
{"type":"message","id":"6edd8fa8","parentId":"71c8fbc5","timestamp":"2026-04-03T17:47:47.213Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0f1f1c402b33ed570169cffd3cf1b481919b90d3e06e00cb5f\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpz_094hZ3A8wwyjUrTOf0K9emPdgv3ftIJzkQGzub2kwQInBlkold1mdTBk6z9Cnq0JNOcvC7AHBUToAPeg7vemncwtLxlqFakyPluFShvB9rxU5jihPx8aMNkZSGQ9Gz9Ow7voHB5fEfMi79eMmZPWhizECj7G39QEieJusbeXdaG2Vxqak16Fjd2vNFuA2biHlEuWBIxXztqFDU3dl_vJo98GgJjYt4BYXbJcHeYBDLnUmGqNOmHv1AuNqNMm_rErYCMB0aKqJeAdi-4H3bk7OBViYVvJ1CO_zQv3QdgDTAySbO8TVCnMF4FvzazGJrS1L03AFTfq6BxqUWzG6CqdoAEJqW7qXO7T5rSW8nswnrX0dIkkzITFX7tEutl3YtvWnJFRm3wGGFE2Az6bXrif5j8Ccz699F8LpIXCOleniw0VNYy2Bjoy-vurcQ_0xo8_lybhzsscjbM4z-k2ArPY21EoE87YNgC9ZqrL5tq-COnfOqREM07lQ9LqKHpwok7uY8EhGIR-ZeJ3vXbL2RcTWHmpgUlV8t6zNatQKY1ZTYwz7T1zWn4j-67HZYmdI_Q-QnweX8MIFa6pokabpAbajXmxrHUSWwGKBSHseZBbU-7kpf1x1HjwKFqbb3E9RiKIx_iyFAz9tDLr9_v2PoMbrWK2PfXAVODWbT0z-NWH5-X3U90eipuKT4AayHku2HMS6CllG4PbQL0w15Lq6rH8VuwAtX5NRCG79cz8uRHPyyQ21-ThLes1DAQwQWBWJRpQJICsTnW3NcA64KE0N2v6kcBie-6fVPFf83GUBAg38aiDvr3CR3oWO-Q7SL2XvWdlw03DLCFq_kE_N-7T9UdN_-w72Wsuqjac8CWBKCh58fsjRllI4pm5zI-TQJfxPPNs7jee25-lcI3_8PzzmvkunjFA==\",\"summary\":[]}"},{"type":"text","text":"Vou fixar isto nos docs do supervisor para reduzir a chance de regressão: deixar explícito que o hop canónico é `exec -> openclaw agent --agent ... --json`, e que ACP não é o caminho desta fase.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0f1f1c402b33ed570169cffd3d9da481919f9c8f9d6915a7a9\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_qEkzWEywkmTV7OAQS8XyhGbb|fc_0f1f1c402b33ed570169cffd3e60a88191a037ddf4b25fb89e","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\MISSION.md","edits":[{"oldText":"Deves:\n- validar o bootstrap recebido\n- assumir formalmente o sector\n- resolver o activation plan\n- preparar dispatch payloads dos operators\n- invocar os 